ll}, {"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.ProxiedInstanceMixin.__delattr__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Delegates attribute access to a lazily created instance.\n\nThe lazily created instance is held in `self._proxied_instance`.\n\n`object.__setattr__(self, '_proxied_instance', None)` should be\nthe first thing executed in the constructor (to avoid infinite\nrecursion).\n\nSetting `self._proxied_instance` to anything different than `None`\nprevents any further attribute assignments on `self` (they will go\nto the proxied instance instead)."]}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin", "bases": ["ProxiedInstanceMixin"], "methods": [{"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "config_prefix", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "**options", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.init_app", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["This method can be used to initialize an application for the use\nwith this broker. A broker can not be used in the context of\nan application unless it is initialized that way.\n\n{meth}`init_app` is called automatically if an `app`\nargument is passed to the constructor.\n"]}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.set_default", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Configure this broker instance to be the global broker instance.\n\nCalls {func}`dramatiq.set_broker` internally.\n"]}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.actor", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "fn", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "**kw", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Declare an actor for this broker instance.\n\nCalls {func}`dramatiq.actor` internally.\n\nExample:\n\n```\nfrom flask_melodramatiq import Broker\n\nbroker = Broker()\n\n@broker.actor\ndef task():\n    print('Snakes appreciate good theatrical preformace.')\n```\n"]}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.actor_options", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.add_middleware", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "middleware", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "before", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "after", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.__get_primary_options", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.__get_secondary_options", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.__merge_options", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "primary", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "secondary", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyBrokerMixin.__get_configuration", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Turns a regular dramatiq broker class into a lazy broker class.\n\nThe derived lazy broker class should be registered with the\n`register_broker_class` function. The derived lazy broker class\nshould define the following additional attribute:\n\n* `_dramatiq_broker_factory`: a callable that returns instances of\n  the regular dramatiq broker class.\n\nThe class `Broker` is the only exception to this rule. It\nrepresents a broker of dynamically configurable type, and can not\nbe registered with `register_broker_class`."]}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyActor", "bases": ["ProxiedInstanceMixin", "dramatiq.Actor"], "methods": [{"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyActor.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "fn", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "broker", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**kw", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyActor.__call__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "*args", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.LazyActor._register_proxied_instance", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "broker", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["A lazily registered actor."]}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.AppContextMiddleware", "bases": ["dramatiq.Middleware"], "methods": [{"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.AppContextMiddleware.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.AppContextMiddleware.before_process_message", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "broker", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "message", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.AppContextMiddleware.after_process_message", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "broker", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "message", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "result", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "exception", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.AppContextMiddleware.state", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.AppContextMiddleware.after_skip_message", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.MultipleAppsWarningMiddleware", "bases": ["dramatiq.Middleware"], "methods": [{"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.MultipleAppsWarningMiddleware.after_process_boot", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "broker", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "flask_melodramatiq.lazy_broker.Broker", "bases": ["La